Requirements:
    - inotify
    - libcurl
Configure file: 
    - specify configure file in command line option
    - important config info in configure file: 
        + vod_dir: dir that will be monitored
        + adm_update_url: url that will be used to update to cms
Log output:
    - Syslog, LOCAL1
    - Filter INFO messages into a separated file for monitoring file upload history
